CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Tarsus Pharmaceuticals Inc is a late clinical-stage biopharmaceutical company. It is focused on the development and commercialization of first-in-class therapeutic candidates to provide treatment for ophthalmic conditions. The company's lead candidate TP-03, is a novel drug that targets the Demodex mite nervous system to kill the mites.
